block.biomancy.creator: Flesh Crucible
death.attack.biomancy.chest_bite: %1$s tried touching a chest but was eaten instead
death.attack.biomancy.creator_spikes: %1$s angered the Maykrs and was impaled by bone spikes
death.attack.biomancy.tooth_projectile: %1$s was forcefully implanted with teeth by %2$s
death.attack.biomancy.tooth_projectile.i: %1$s received a lethal dental implant by %2$s using %3$s
death.attack.biomancy.corrosive_acid_pro: %1$s was doused with corrosive acid by %2$s
%1$s was showered in corrosive acid by %2$s using %3$s
tooltip.biomancy.mob_fang: Cutting tooth made of Bone tissue rich in Bio-Minerals.
tooltip.biomancy.mob_claw: Hardened Claw made of tough fibers and rich in Bio-Minerals.
tooltip.biomancy.mob_marrow: Marrow extracted from the bones of your victims. Rich in Hormones and Bio-Minerals.
tooltip.biomancy.withered_mob_marrow:
Withered Marrow, some dark fluid is oozing out of it.
Maybe you should suck it dry...
tooltip.biomancy.mob_gland: Organ sac filled with bile to the brim.
tooltip.biomancy.volatile_gland:
Gland filled with a reactive fluid.
Seems safe to drink...
tooltip.biomancy.toxin_gland: A organ full of toxin, maybe you should drink this...
tooltip.biomancy.creator: Offer adequate Tributes to the Flesh Lord, and summon forth primordial messengers of exquisite flesh.
tooltip.biomancy.digester: A machine born from flesh that converts food and plants into nutrients.
tooltip.biomancy.decomposer:
A bio-machine that deconstructs items into their base components.
The bio-machine consumes nutrients to function.
tooltip.biomancy.tongue: Extracts up to 3 items of the same type every 24 ticks from containers its attached to and drops them on the ground.
tooltip.biomancy.fleshkin_chest:
A fleshkin forged into the shape of a chest with sharp teeth and a resilient stomach allowing it to keeps its contents when mined.
Only its master may open and takes its content without repercussion.

It's fangs look awfully sharp...
tooltip.biomancy.fleshkin_pressure_plate:
Fleshkin pancake. Yummy...
It has two behaviors, either it only activates for its owner or it only works for everyone else.

Sneak click to change its behavior.
tooltip.biomancy.storage_sac: Cheap Shulker-like storage sac that also works like a bundle.
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_door: A sliding door made of flesh...
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_fence: Fence made of bones and flesh...
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_fence_gate: Fence gate made of bones and flesh...
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_iris_door: Trapdoor-like iris door made of flesh...
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_ladder: Ladder mainly made of bones and a little bit of flesh...
tooltip.biomancy.flesh: A generic block of flesh... Don't bother me with this!
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_slab: A generic slab of flesh... Don't bother me with this!
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_stairs: Stairs made of generic flesh... Don't bother me with this!
tooltip.biomancy.packed_flesh: Tenacious Block of flesh. Is it tough enough?
tooltip.biomancy.packed_flesh_slab: Tenacious Slab of flesh. Is it tough enough?
tooltip.biomancy.packed_flesh_stairs: Stairs made of tenacious flesh. Is it tough enough?
tooltip.biomancy.primal_flesh: Primitive and pure, you better not touch this with your dirty paws.
tooltip.biomancy.primal_flesh_slab: Primitive and pure, you better not touch this with your dirty paws.
tooltip.biomancy.corrupted_primal_flesh: It's no longer pure... Don't deny it. Your dirty paws caused this!
tooltip.biomancy.corrupted_primal_flesh_: It's no longer pure... Don't deny it. Your dirty paws caused this!
tooltip.biomancy.malignant_flesh: Looks dangerous, you better not touch this!
tooltip.biomancy.malignant_flesh_slab: Looks dangerous, you better not touch this!
tooltip.biomancy.malignant_flesh_veins: Looks dangerous, you better not touch this!
tooltip.biomancy.flesh_bits: A tiny bit of flesh... Used as a primary crafting ingredient.
tooltip.biomancy.bone_scraps: A tiny fragment of bone... Provides rigidity and shape to flesh. Useful for assembling mechanical parts.
tooltip.biomancy.tough_fibers: Fibrous tissue that is very tough and rigid. Useful for crafting things that need more resilience.
tooltip.biomancy.elastic_fibers: Fibrous tissue that is sturdy but has rubbery properties. It appears like a good material to imitate muscles.
tooltip.biomancy.mineral_fragments:
Component only obtained in Decomposer.
Used to harden fibers.
tooltip.biomancy.bio_minerals:
Component only obtained in Decomposer.
Used to toughen fibers.
tooltip.biomancy.gem_fragments: Used to enhance hardened fibers to their maximum resilience, very expensive.
tooltip.biomancy.stone_powder: Very Basic Crafting component, usually obtained as a byproduct from decomposing things.
tooltip.biomancy.bio_lumens:
Basic component, only obtained via the Decomposer, usually alongside biotic matter.

Used as a cosmetic upgrade to make things glow.
tooltip.biomancy.exotic_dust: Exotic substance, maybe magical. Byproduct from decomposing magical things.
tooltip.biomancy.fertilizer: Fertilizer that induces hyper-growth in plants, even for reeds, cactus, nether wart and chorus plant.
tooltip.biomancy.injector: A simple device which utilizes a razor sharp needle to quickly and forcefully inject Serums into Mobs and Players.
tooltip.biomancy.growth_serum: Induces growth, in most cases child Mobs grow into Adults.
tooltip.biomancy.rejuvenation_serum: Reverses the growth of Mobs, in most cases they turn into children.
tooltip.biomancy.breeding_stimulant: Makes Animals hyper-fertile, making them able to constantly reproduce for a short time.
tooltip.biomancy.absorption_boost: Grants stackable absorption health points for Mobs and Players.
tooltip.biomancy.insomnia_cure: Resets the last slept time, no need to sleep for quite some time.
tooltip.biomancy.cleansing_serum: Removes all potion effects from a Mob or Player.
tooltip.biomancy.decay_agent: Causes a disease that eats away at the flesh and strongly affects zombies.
tooltip.biomancy.adrenaline_serum: Floods your body with additional Adrenaline giving you a temporary power boost for a price...
tooltip.biomancy.organic_compound: Slimy substance made of bile infused with nutrients.
tooltip.biomancy.exotic_compound: Substance of a questionable nature, comprised of exotic material and other trace elements.
tooltip.biomancy.unstable_compound: Very unstable and reactive substance. Seems like it will combust if it comes in contact with other things.
tooltip.biomancy.genetic_compound: Cocktail of various hormones, nutrients and organic elements. Compound that seems useful for producing potent drugs.
tooltip.biomancy.healing_additive: An highly concentrated substance that is used to imbue it properties to other compounds.
tooltip.biomancy.corrosive_additive: An highly corrosive fluid that seems useful for alchemically burning away organic material or weakening the bonds of complex substances.
tooltip.biomancy.creator_mix: A meal made for the Maykrs... just not for you.
tooltip.biomancy.glass_vial: Glass is transparent... very brittle, yet strong and rigid. Very high alchemical resistance, seems perfect for holding reactive substances.
tooltip.biomancy.organic_matter: Moist organic material, extracted from Plants. With its dark and fibrous texture almost seems like humus.
tooltip.biomancy.nutrients: Very hard pellets rich in energy, almost look like vitamin pills. Occasional byproduct from decomposing plants, but mainly obtained from digesting plants.
tooltip.biomancy.nutrient_paste: Nutrients combined with Biotic Matter to moisten the hard pellets and get a paste. Almost looks like yellowish cake, a useful source of energy.
tooltip.biomancy.nutrient_bar: Compressed Nutrient Paste into the shape of an edible Bar.
tooltip.biomancy.serum: Some kind of exotic substance affecting Mobs.
tooltip.biomancy.bile_spitter:
WIP: "living" projectile weapon that shoots corrosive bile.
Intended behaviour: charge it like a bow to increase damage & size of projectile.
tooltip.biomancy.long_claws:
WIP: Claw with higher attack distance. Excite the weapon with kills and it will extends its claws.
Special Effect: pull user or victim depending on weight difference.
tooltip.biomancy.living_flesh:
It's alive!
But it looks too dumb to be the brain of a mob. You should turn it into a construct.
tooltip.biomancy.hormone_secretion: A fluid extract very rich in hormones. Potent material for making drugs.
tooltip.biomancy.withering_ooze: Corrosive extract, might have a bio-alchemical use.
tooltip.biomancy.volatile_fluid: Combustible extract, needs further processing to be more dangerous.
tooltip.biomancy.bile: Organic base material which is often used in bio-alchemy.
tooltip.biomancy.regenerative_fluid: Fluid that has regenerative properties, used to concoct healing additives.
advancements.biomancy.root.title: Meat Whisperer
advancements.biomancy.root.description: You feel a presence in the flesh, it whispers into your ears: "Raw Meat is useful..."
advancements.biomancy.flesh.title: Strange Vision
advancements.biomancy.flesh.description: You felt a foreign presence from the ender eye. A cauldron made of raw meat appears in your mind, you start forgetting portals... you feel compelled to build it...
advancements.biomancy.living_flesh.title: Reviving Flesh
advancements.biomancy.living_flesh.descr: Use the Flesh Crucible to sacrifice organic things to the strange presence and revive dead meat. It's seems like fluids enriched in life energy are needed.
advancements.biomancy.decomposer.title: Munch & Crunch
advancements.biomancy.decomposer.descrip: You suddenly feel disgusted by the composter. You should use a semi-living construct to decompose things into their base parts.
advancements.biomancy.bio_forge.title: Organic Smithing
advancements.biomancy.bio_forge.descript: You dreamt of a Bio-Construct weaving organic parts together into intricate semi-living things... You don't know when, but you built it.
advancements.biomancy.digester.title: Yummy Paste
advancements.biomancy.digester.descripti: You feel tired of feeding your Bio-Constructs with poor quality food. You have the urge to produce a nutrients enriched yellow-green paste.
advancements.biomancy.bio_lab.title: Is this still Alchemy?
advancements.biomancy.bio_lab.descriptio: You had an epiphany, why use crude inorganic tools to brew potions if an Bio-Construct can do it better. No longer do you need to mix or adjust the heat by yourself.
advancements.biomancy.compounds.title: Organic Alchemy
advancements.biomancy.compounds.descript: Combine various organic secretions and substances to create Compounds and Serums.
death.attack.biomancy.blight_thorn.item: %1$s was mauled to death by %2$s using %3$s
death.attack.biomancy.ravenous_hunger: %1$s couldn't stop their ravenous hunger and consumed themselves
death.attack.biomancy.disease.player: %1$s was infected by an disease through %2$s and ultimately died
